meta {
  name: Ready
  type: http
  seq: 2
}

get {
  url: {{sidecarBaseUrl}}/ready
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
}

docs {
  ## Sidecar readiness

  Hard deps: gateway reachable + `OPENROUTER_API_KEY` present.
  Soft fields: `openrouter.reachable`, `langsmith` — never alone flip `ready`.
  Does **not** probe openFDA/DailyMed.

  **HTTP 503** when `ready: false` (orchestrators that key off status alone see degradation).
  Body still returns the readiness JSON.
}
